 news|url=http://wenhui.news365.com.cn/html/2016-08/16/content_456180.html|title=领跑者“墨子号”———团队融合助中国在量子科学领域占得先机|date=2016-08-46|access-date=2016-08-19|newspaper=文匯报|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190206145009/http://wenhui.news365.com.cn/html/2016-08/16/content_456180.html|archive-date=2019-02-06|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

