roller%5D=News&tx_news_pi1%5Baction%5D=detail&cHash=08f8ec239b7dbaff477eb02ad2ff70b4|title=FIRST QUANTUM SATELLITE SUCCESSFULLY LAUNCHED|publisher=Austrian Academy of Sciences|language=en|date=2016-08-16|access-date=2016-08-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305002336/http://www.oeaw.ac.at/en/austrian-academy-of-sciences/the-oeaw/article/neu/?tx_news_pi1%5Bcontroller%5D=News&tx_news_pi1%5Baction%5D=detail&cHash=08f8ec239b7dbaff477eb02ad2ff70b4|archive-date=2017-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

